        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-4 order-3 text-center" style="margin-top: 120px;">
            <h2 style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; color: orange; font-weight: bold;">Search and Explore</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 25px; width: 80%; margin: 0 auto; margin-top: 20px; font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
                Browse through various reviews from other interns and explore to find the best fit for you!
                <a asp-controller="Reviews" asp-action="Index" style="color: orange;">Search now</a> to get started!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1 order-1 text-center" style="margin-top: 120px;">
            <h2 style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; color: orange; font-weight: bold;">Blog</h2>
            <p style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; font-size: 25px; width: 80%; margin: 0 auto; margin-top: 20px;">Interested in sharing your unique internship experiences or delving into the stories shared by others? 
                Check out our <a asp-controller="Blogs" asp-action="Index" style="color: orange;">blog page</a>!
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2 order-2 text-center" style="margin-top: 40px;">
            <img src="image/blog2.jpeg" class="img-fluid" alt="Image Description" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; border-radius: 10px;">
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


